{"tid":1259194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手機內有數百張「胸肌及陽具特寫照片」 25歲姓林實習男醫生被控遊蕩","createTime":"2019-06-26T13:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T08:38:34.000Z","uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c632bbd8b4cd0797c15f2b66b4832b4c97af3f31","tid":1259194,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"25歲姓林實習男醫生早前被發現偷拍男護及男病人被捕，他被暫控一項遊蕩罪，案件下月9日在東區裁判法院提訊。瑪麗醫院發言人表示，案件已進入司法程序，不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n案發於1月11日，瑪麗醫院一名男護士在護士宿舍洗澡期間，發現遭人偷拍報警。警方經翻查大廈閉路電視片段，翌日拘捕林某，調查期間發現其手機及電腦藏有數百張男病人私處照片，部位包括胸口及陽具，並發現至少兩名被拍者去年底曾入住明愛醫院，相信住院期間被偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偷拍都只係遊蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ed5659d5fc3938d0bb4b9432cb9ccc2c4ed3fa","tid":1259194,"uid":257184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"要岀動催淚彈同布袋彈"},{"pid":"febf280bddec324dc5aa08e4d1d517ca64ecc9b2","tid":1259194,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n［突發］中環要人！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258994</a><br />\n[突發]今日626集會後全民行山！ 攻頂計劃！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258698</a><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"5cb2e55bdf75cb0a399b68dd07d0f8ec9e0339e9","tid":1259194,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"遊行又被控遊蕩，總之係街睇你唔順眼就係遊蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a091c349857ba568de8dba7dd3f5c1af6708da","tid":1259194,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"怒漢